description: In front of a hospital I almost bumped into a guy looking at his cellphone. He had a bandaged arm, which looked like a nice conversation opener. It turned out that he got injured in the warehouse where he worked. In the Czech Republic you don´t get sickness benefits for the first three days of the sick leave. Which can be very difficult for some people. Fillip, that was the boy´s name, was more than happy to show me some skin to compensate for the lost money. His beautiful chest was worth much more than 500 I paid him. I could say he wasn´t gay, he went through a break-up some time ago, so I had to thread carefully. Was this sweet and innocent angel greedy enough to get really dirty?
title: Czech Hunter 266
